{"tid":1657814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於陳同學既CCTV, 我有D 野發現左","createTime":"2019-10-16T09:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T20:43:47.000Z","uid":37326,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e84ea1b4d21b8cab7ae5b5416d5dda0ec3516aff","tid":1657814,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:08:58.000Z","msg":"我有D 野想講, 可以睇一睇<br />\n<br />\n首先我睇晒今日公怖既CCTV<br />\n有公段時間既片應該係校方仲未公開<br />\n1. 由佢出LIFT, 到係2/F 出現手上既文件同電話唔知咩原因唔見左 呢段時間有成差唔多20分鐘<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(仲有一野大家忽略左既物件, 陳同學入LIFT果陣條頸係掛住一個疑似紅色證件套既野, 都係唔見左)</span></span></strong></span><br />\n2. 由佢係9/F 再上一層, 對鞋離奇唔見左, 呢度又有成7分鐘<br />\n既然佢真係有咁多鏡頭影到佢之後既行蹤, 冇理由冇左呢20分鐘同7分鐘既野, 而且兩段時間陳同學都有野唔見左<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(呢度我又發現到D 野, 係時間18:28:51, 陳同學曾經停左望左自己對鞋幾眼)</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我認為呢兩段時間極為重要, HKDI 應該係有野隱瞞, 希望各位再逼HKDI 再交出餘下既片段!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c69d5dfea8b4371b7ddf68361e74842710680a65","tid":1657814,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"91189a07696ce0ca66193b08e335d58614df26ae","tid":1657814,"uid":37326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4eadcf00a620049dae4ce3b56b5cf98cbd541217","tid":1657814,"uid":320943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:36:59.000Z","msg":"推 同你發現同一樣野 雖然未必係重要線索 不過細節都唔應該忽略<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCdcwGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxC